<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạlrb hw ʿznạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạlrãbũ hūa ʿizũnā
 fabihi nasẖ̊baʿu
 wakulũ ʿiziⁿ̃ gẖaẙrahu
 lạa budã yun̊zaʿu

[V2]
 2- fayā lagẖib̊ṭaẗiⁿ lanā
 biʿizĩnā ạl̊mum̊tāz̊
 famaʿ̊hu nil̊nā sẖir̊kaẗaⁿ
 lanā bihā ạm̊tīāz̊

[V3]
 3- yā laẙta bihi naq̊naʿu
 wanas̊ʿay̱ biạlại̹ymān̊
 falạ naʿūda nukẖ̊daʿu
 biạl̊buṭ̊li wāl̊ʿīān̊

[V4]
 4- ại̹dẖ̊ maʿ̊hu saẘfa naj̊lisu
 wanaḥ̊ẓay̱ biạl̊kamāl̊
 nan̊ẓuruhu mukalãlạaⁿ
 biạl̊maj̊di wāl̊jalạl̊</lyrics>
</song>